Zahra Cheeseman (Arabic; amụrụ na 8 Nọvemba 2002) bụ onye Morocco a mụrụ n'England nke na agba bọọlụ dị ka onye na edebe goolu maka otu kọleji Amerika Colorado College Tigers na otu ụmụ nwanyị Morocco.
A zụlitere Cheeseman na Haywards Heath. Nna ya bụ onye Bekee na nne ya bụ onye Morocco.
Cheeseman gara Colorado College na United steeti.
Cheeseman bụ ngwaahịa Brighton. Ọ nọkwa na Ụlọ akwụkwọ Charlton. Ọ sonyeere Lewes na 2020.
Cheeseman mere nke mbụ ya na Morocco na 14 Junnu 2021 na mmeri enyi na enyi n'ụlọ 3 na Mali.
